---
import { whatsappLink, messages } from '../../utils/whatsapp'
---
<div class="orcamento-block">
  <span class="arrow-down" aria-hidden="true">
    <svg width="32" height="48" viewBox="0 0 32 48" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <path d="M16 4 L16 38" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-dasharray="3 5" />
      <path d="M6 30 L16 42 L26 30" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" fill="none" />
    </svg>
  </span>
  <h3>Cada negócio é único, <em>cada plano também.</em></h3>
  <p>Conversa rápida no WhatsApp pra entender qual combinação faz sentido pro seu momento. Sem compromisso, sem script.</p>
  <a href={whatsappLink(messages.hubGeneric)} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="cta-primary">solicitar orçamento</a>
  <a href={whatsappLink(messages.helpChoose)} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="cta-secondary">ainda em dúvida? conversa rápida no whats</a>
</div>

<style>
.orcamento-block { margin: var(--space-12) auto 0; padding: var(--space-12) var(--space-8) var(--space-8); background: var(--grad-soft-teal); border-radius: 16px; text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgba(0,161,152,0.18); max-width: 640px; position: relative; }
.arrow-down { display: inline-flex; color: var(--rec-teal); margin-bottom: var(--space-4); animation: arrow-bob 2.4s ease-in-out infinite; }
@keyframes arrow-bob {
  0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
  50% { transform: translateY(6px); }
}
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  .arrow-down { animation: none; }
}
.orcamento-block h3 { margin-bottom: var(--space-3); font-size: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.2; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: var(--letter-tight); }
.orcamento-block h3 em { color: var(--rec-teal); font-style: italic; }
.orcamento-block p { margin-bottom: var(--space-6); color: #556; max-width: 480px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; line-height: 1.6; }
.cta-primary { display: inline-block; background: var(--rec-purple); color: #fff; padding: 16px 36px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-bottom: var(--space-4); transition: transform var(--motion-fast) var(--easing), box-shadow var(--motion-fast) var(--easing); box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(62,64,149,0.18); }
.cta-primary:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(62,64,149,0.28); background: var(--rec-teal); }
.cta-secondary { display: block; color: var(--rec-teal); font-size: var(--type-small); font-weight: 600; }
.cta-secondary:hover { color: var(--rec-purple); }
</style>
